Title

Data Transformation

Content

Introduction

Raw data was transformed into a format suitable for visualization in Tableau.

Transformation Performed

Imported CSV into MySQL.
Connected Tableau with the dataset.
Changed data types where required.
Converted numerical measures into appropriate aggregations such as COUNT and AVG.
Created age-wise and cholesterol-based visualizations.
Used filters for gender, age, chest pain, and heart disease.

Outcome

The transformed data was successfully used to create interactive dashboards.